rekindling_passion_research: Ukuphinde uvuse uthando kuvuselela ubudlelwano. Izifundo zaseNyuvesi yaseChicago zikhombisa ukuthi imizamo eqondile yokuvuselela uthando iholela ekwanelisekeni kobudlelwano nasekubuyiseleni uxhumano lomzwelo.
rekindling_passion_statistics: INemlys isiza ukuvuselela uthando ngezigameko ezingaphezu kuka-30 zomdlandla nothando njalo ngenyanga.
introducing_healthy_habits_description: Yamukele futhi ugcine izindlela zokuphila eziphilile njengethimba. Lolu hambo lukukhuthaza ukuthi nikhuthazane ekuphuculeni inhlalakahle ngokuzivocavoca nesimo sengqondo esihle.
introducing_healthy_habits_research: Ukuzibandakanya ezimilweni eziphilile ndawonye kwandisa ukwesekwa kanye nempilo enhle. Izifundo zaseNyuvesi yaseCambridge zikhombisa ukuthi ama-couples abambe iqhaza ezimweni zokuziphatha eziphilile ndawonye ahlangabezana nokwaneliseka kobudlelwano obukhulu kanye nemiphumela engcono empilweni yomuntu.
introducing_healthy_habits_statistics: INemlys ikhuthaza ama-couples ukuthi amukele imikhuba ephilile engaphezu kuka-5 ukuze bathuthukise izindlela zokuphila phakathi nenyanga.
preparing_for_children_description: Zilungiselele ukwamukela umndeni. Lolu hambo luhilela ukuxoxa ngezinhlobo zokuba abazali, okulindelwe, kanye nezinhlelo zokuqinisekisa ukuthi wonke umuntu uhamba ngezindlela ezifanayo ekukhuliseni abantwana.
preparing_for_children_research: Ukulungiselela ubu-ntwana kuqinisa ubudlelwano bomndeni. Izifundo zaseNyuvesi yasePennsylvania ziveza ukuthi ama-couples ahlangene ezinhlelweni zokuba abazali enza uguquko abe lula futhi kube nomndeni ohlelwe kahle.
preparing_for_children_statistics: INemlys ihola ama-couples ekulungiseleleni abantwana ngezingxoxo namaqhinga aqondile angaphezu kuka-30 njalo ngenyanga.
preparing_for_marriage_description: Yakha isisekelo esiqinile somshado. Lolu hambo luhlola ukuzinikela kwakho, izinhloso enizabelana ngazo, kanye nokulindelwe ukuze kuqinisekiswe umshado oqinile nowaneleyo.
preparing_for_marriage_research: Ukulungiselela umshado kuholela ekuqiniseni izisekelo zomshado. Ucwaningo oluvela eNyuvesi yaseNorthwestern lubonisa ukuthi izithandani ezilungiselela ngokucophelela zibhekana nohlukaniso oluncane nolwaneliseka komshado oluphakeme.
preparing_for_marriage_statistics: INemlys iqondisa izithandani ekulungiseleleni umshado ngokusebenzisa izingxoxo ezisebenzisekayo ezingaphezu kuka-20 kanye nezenzo njalo ngenyanga.
plan_no_personal_plan: Alukho uhlelo lomuntu siqu olutholakele. Sicela udale olunye.
v3_premium_review_1_description: Ngisebenzisa iNemlys nentombi yami lapho sesiphuthelwe izinto zokuxoxa. Kukhona okuqukethwe okuningi okusizayo ku-app, futhi kusenza sizizwe seduze. Siyafunda okuningi ngomunye nomunye.
v3_premium_review_2_description: INemlys ikahle kithi uma sisohlukene. Isinikeza izihloko esingavamisile ukuzixoxa, ngakho kuzizwa sengathi sixhumene ngokujulile :)
v3_premium_review_3_description: Mina nomfana wami siyawuthanda umjuluko wokuqukethwe. Singakhetha ukuthi yini esifuna ukuyenza namhlanje, futhi njalo kuvusa ingxoxo enenjongo. Uhlelo lusebenza kalula futhi luyasebenziseka, okungikwenza ngikuthokozise.
leave_couple_confirmation_message: Uqinisekile ukuthi ufuna ukushiya ubudlelwano bakho bamanje?
leave_couple_error_message: Kwenzeke iphutha lapho uzama ukushiya ubudlelwano. Sicela uzame futhi kamuva.
v3_home_turn_on_notification: Izaziso zakho zime. Zivule ukuze uthole izikhumbuzo.
v3_upgrade_text: Zama izinkulungwane zemidlalo emisha, izivivinyo, ukuhlolwa, imisebenzi, izindatshana kanye nemibuzo. Ungashintsha emuva nganoma isiphi isikhathi kuzilungiselelo.
content_feedback_help: Umbono wakho usisiza ukuthuthukisa okuqukethwe kwethu
notification_pre_content_2_body: Bheka imibono yakamuva yedethi nemisebenzi ezoyisa wena nothandekayo wakho ezingeni elilandelayo.
notification_daily_content_1_body: Ngena inselelweni yanamuhla bese usebenzisa lo mbuzo ongajwayelekile ukuvusa izingxoxo ezimnandi no{{partnerName}}.
notification_daily_content_2_body: Khuphula indaba yothando lwakho—ngena ohambweni lwakho olwenziwe ngokukhethekile olugcwele injabulo, izinto ezingajwayelekile, nezikhathi ezishisayo zothando wena no{{partnerName}}.
notification_daily_content_3_body: Uhlelo lwakho lwansuku zonke selukhishwe—lugcwele izimanga ezingajwayelekile ukuvusa izingxoxo ezimnandi no{{partnerName}}.
notification_daily_content_4_body: Gcoba lowo mlilo—okuqukethwe namuhla likulungele ukuvusa injabulo nemizwa yokudlala.
notification_daily_content_5_body: Ngena endaweni yemizwa—umbuzo, umdlalo noma isivivinyo samuhla sikulungele ukugcina wena no-{{partnerName}} nihambe kuloluhlelo lokuxhumana.
notification_daily_content_6_body: Thatha ikhefu lokuphumula—phendula umbuzo osikhethe wona bese udlala ngemizwa no-{{partnerName}} ngokujulile.
notification_daily_content_7_body: Bheka isimanga esisihlele wena no-{{partnerName}}—umbuzo namuhla uzokwenza ujabule.
notification_inactivity_1_body: Sekuphele izinsuku ezi-3—buya, thatha okuqukethwe okusha, bese uxhuma no-{{partnerName}}.
notification_inactivity_2_body: Sekuphele izinsuku ezi-7—sikukhumbula wena no-{{partnerName}}. Buya ngokushesha, kungenjalo i-CEO yethu ingase iqale ukukhala.
notification_inactivity_3_body: Izinsuku eziyi-14 zotule, hawu! Phula imodi yokungatholakali bese uzibandakanya emisebenzini ejabulisayo no-{{partnerName}}.
notification_inactivity_4_body: Uma uNemlys wayengumdlalo weTamagotchi, manje-ke sekuyiphela impela. Buya futhi unike ubudlelwane bakho uthando.
notification_inactivity_5_body: 60 izinsuku? I-FOMO enkulu! Wena no-{{partnerName}} nisashisa—buya futhi nikhanyise uhlelo.
notification_inactivity_6_body: Izinyanga ezi-3 sezidlulile? Buyisela umoya wakho bese uvusa imizuzu emisha no-{{partnerName}}.
notification_inactivity_7_body: Izinyanga ezi-6 zokungasebenzi, {{firstName}}? Buya futhi ubuke okuqukethwe okusha ukuze ugcine ubudlelwane bakho bushisa no-{{partnerName}}.
notification_inactivity_8_body: Unyaka ungaphandle? Sekuyisikhathi sokuvuselela umlilo no-{{partnerName}} nokudala izinkumbulo ezintsha ezimangalisayo. Sikhumbule wena!
onboarding_quiz_question_1_2: Cabanga ubusuku bokudate obuhle nobabili. Ufuna ukwenza ini ngalo?
onboarding_quiz_question_1_option_1_havi: Hleka, phumuza, futhi udale izinkumbulo ezimnandi
onboarding_quiz_question_1_option_2_unde: Qinisekisa ukuthi izimiso eziyisisekelo zethu ziyahambisana
onboarding_quiz_question_2_2: Yiphi ingxenye ofuna ukuyihlola ngokujulile ebudlelwaneni benu?
onboarding_quiz_question_3_2: Yini engasiza ukuthi nizizwe nisondene nakakhulu?
onboarding_quiz_question_4_2: Uma ungasheshisa ukuthuthukisa ingxenye eyodwa yobudlelwano benu, iyoba yini?
onboarding_quiz_question_4_option_3_havi: Nibe nocansi futhi nixoxe ngalo ngokwengeziwe
onboarding_quiz_question_6_2: Yini imikhuba emisha ofuna ukuyiqala ndawonye?
onboarding_quiz_question_6_option_1_gett: Yabelana ngemibono nezibuyekezo zempilo nsuku zonke
onboarding_quiz_question_6_option_2_havi: Hlela izinsuku zokuhlangana ezithokozisayo njalo ngesonto
onboarding_quiz_question_6_option_4_plan: Hlela izigigaba ezinkulu zempilo njalo ngenyanga
premium_charge_conditions: Imali yonyaka engu-{{price}} izokhishwa ngemva kokuqedwa kwesivivinyo samahhala ngo-{{date}}. Akukho ukuzibophezela, ungakhansela noma nini
notification_streak_1_body_2: Usendleleni yokulandelelana kwezinsuku eziyi-{{streakDay}}! Sekusele amahora angu-2 kuphela ukuze ugcine umlilo wakho ushisa!
notification_streak_2_body_2: I-streak yakho iye yaqina. Ngena namuhla ukuze uqhubeke nokuthuthukisa indaba yothando lwenu!
notification_streak_3_body_2: I-streak yakho iphelelwe yisikhathi, qala futhi namuhla ukuze ubuyele esimweni esihle nobudlelwane benu!
v3_home_finished_free_2_description: Buyela kusasa ukuze uthole uhlelo olusha lwamahhala lwanamuhla noma uvule konke okuqukethwe manje
v3_home_finished_premium_2_description: Buyela kusasa ukuze uthole uhlelo olusha lwanamuhla noma uhlolisise konke okuqukethwe manje
notification_pre_content_1_body: Ngena kokuqukethwe kwethu bese uvuselela impilo yakho yothando. INemlys ilapha ukuze ithuthukise izinhloso zenu zobudlelwano.
premium_unlimited_content_title: Vula yonke imibuzo, izivivinyo, imidlalo, ukuhlolwa, imisebenzi yokuzivocavoca nezindatshana
